    "The study's emphasis on quantitative bibliometric indicators may have overlooked the interdisciplinary nature and practical application of GeoGebra research in mathematics education.",
    "Encouraging interdisciplinary approaches that integrate methods and theories from other fields could effectively address the complex educational issues surrounding the use of GeoGebra.",
    "In summary, the present study offers valuable insights, yet the identified limitations suggest avenues for future research to explore the dynamic, interdisciplinary, and practical aspects of GeoGebra research in mathematics education more comprehensively.",
